'http://www.islamhouse.com/p/268433',
'http://d1.islamhouse.com/data/ar/ih_books/single4/ar_atthamar_almogtana.pdf,http://d1.islamhouse.com/data/ar/ih_books/single4/ar_atthamar_almogtana.doc',
'سعيد بن علي بن وهف القحطاني',
