'http://www.islamhouse.com/p/209003',
'http://d1.islamhouse.com/data/ar/ih_books/single2/ar_understanding_of_causes_of_lessons.pdf,http://d1.islamhouse.com/data/ar/ih_books/single2/ar_understanding_of_causes_of_lessons.doc',
